data.review: I just paid $25.11 for a whopper original chicken leg coke and medium onion rings. I ordered the 2 for $5 and got only 1 of each. Ordered 2 whoppers and 2 originals. Plus I’m missing my fries too!!! Then they were microwaving coffee. Worst service!!! I try calling to let them know I’m missing items and no one picks up
